:"아일랜드 카운티 미스","lifeSummary":"Sir Barnaby Cusack(이)가 대략 1348년 아일랜드 디오스스 프 미스에서 태어났을 때, 그의 아버지 John Cusack(은)는 54세였고, 그의 어머니 Joan Geneville(은)는 24세였다. 그는 대략 1370년 아일랜드 카운티 미스에서 Lady Eliza Crompe(와)과 결혼했다. 그들은 적어도 두 명의 아들을 두었다. 그는 아일랜드 카운티 루스 드로민에서 사망했다."},"lv":{"about 1348–":"ap 1348. gadu–miris","1348–Male":"1348–miris","1357–Male":"1357–miris","1361–Male":"1361–miris","–1347":"–1347","–1380":"–1380","–Male":"miris","1353–1390":"1353–1390","1350–Male":"1350.gads–miris","1390–1438":"1390–1438","1295–1386":"1295–1386","1325–Female":"1325–mirusi","about 1370":"ap 1370. gadu","ABT 1356":"ap 1356. gadu","1350":"1350. gads","1295":"1295","1361":"1361","1380":"1380","1390":"1390","1348":"1348","1325":"1325","1347":"1347","1357":"1357","about 1348":"ap 1348. gadu","1386":"1386","1353":"1353","Abt 1390":"ap 1390. gadu","1438":"1438","Gerrardstown, Meath, Leinster, Ireland":"Diocese of Meath, Īrija","Gerrardstown, County Meath, Ireland":"Gerrardstown, County Meath, Īrija","Dromin, Louth, Leinster, Ireland":"Dromin, County Louth, Īrija","County Kildare, Ireland":"County Kildare, Īrija","County Meath, Ireland":"County Meath, Īrija"},"mg":{"about 1348–":"tany ho any amin'ny 1348–Maty","1348–Male":"1348–Maty","1357–Male":"1357–Maty","1361–Male":"1361–Maty","–1347":"–1347","–1380":"–1380","–Male":"Maty","1353–1390":"1353–1390","1350–Male":"1350–Maty","1390–1438":"1390–1438","1295–1386":"1295–1386","1325–Female":"1325–Maty","about 1370":"tany ho any amin'ny 1370","ABT 1356":"tany ho any amin'ny 1356","1350":"1350","1295":"1295","1361":"1361","1380":"1380","1390":"1390","1348":"1348","1325":"1325","1347":"1347","1357":"1357","about 1348":"tany ho any amin'ny 1348","1386":"1386","1353":"1353","Abt 1390":"tany ho any amin'ny 1390","1438":"1438","Gerrardstown, Meath, Leinster, Ireland":"Diocese of Meath, Irlandy","Gerrardstown, County Meath, Ireland":"Gerrardstown, County Meath, Irlandy","Dromin, Louth, Leinster, Ireland":"Dromin, County Louth, Irlandy","County Kildare, Ireland":"Count